:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>City有得教真係好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當年我仲係UG仔個陣，副修中文，個Prof同我講唔夠5個人take所以唔開文心雕龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n下必修喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但都係自己睇書睇論文做present，<br />\n冇乜特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我讀個間 文心雕龍係elective嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁睇野做present, 大學教育係咁上下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 易交代</blockquote><br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 詩經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 短歌行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就係呢d feel喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當年我都係入中文系失敗先要副修<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過都好既，而家讀緊MPhil, 有時間可以自己睇返中文，我都係鍾意古代文學多過現代文學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d854ed86aef4c6b6ba8715e94a401c0f04be19a","tid":429709,"uid":152197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T08:00:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自學o既話我好擔心呢幾個問題<br />\n<br />\n1.自學方向？<br />\n2.點知o岩定錯？好定壞？<br />\n3.點知學習進度？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大學做present一定有一堆參考書目，<br />\n跟住睇跟住做實冇死，<br />\n你可以打個course名睇下佢course outline D參考書目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n例如：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cityu.edu.hk/pg/201718/course/CAH5704.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cityu.edu.hk%2Fpg%2F201718%2Fcourse%2FCAH5704.pdf&d=YWLSRs%2BcVshAsQ1%2FQDMmPaS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=2d99ec5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cityu.edu.hk/pg/201718/course/CAH5704.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"bbda565783ea2eb8b5b3cafe497252c6d853ad8a","tid":429709,"uid":152379,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T08:05:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家做緊阿蘇狗 本科生有咩唔滿意請負皮，然後上一頁<br />\n<br />\n入正題：<br />\n小弟對文史野算幾有興趣，特別啲小學（音韻學）、詩詞歌賦、駢文、古典文獻呢類等，但現代同西方野就真係唔掂<br />\n最初想入大學嘅原因就係想提升呢方面嘅中文水平，達到可以出口成文、揮筆成詩嘅境界。同埋我都幾鍾意創作，例如改詞、寫詩、作故等。但問題就係能力太低，又唔工整又唔詩意，平仄押韻都係自己搞自己學，冇人教冇人討論，根本唔知岩定錯好定壞。<br />\n<br />\n例如想學琴，咁就去琴社跟老師學，自學都得，但一彈琴就會見真章，分高下。所以我從來唔覺自己所識嘅中文係正統，就係因為呢個諗法，而決定一定要入大學學真正嘅野。但無奈抵死入唔到，卒之做返阿蘇，雖然都係想讀果科嘅中文，但開學至今我幾乎搵唔到半點同我想像中有關嘅野，明明個課程叫中國文學，但日日講西方同現代野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 文心雕龍？說文解字？詞林正韻？我都唔撚知去咗邊度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再講就係教學模式，大專黎講似乎都係靠自己搵自己學，tutor/prof.只係從旁指引甚或只係鳩吹<br />\n咁樣變相就係我自己去搞，同我讀之前做嘅野有咩分別？貪你個圖書館夠大？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n近排成日係度諗，知識唔夠，所以就去讀，但讀完都用唔返，或者根本就唔係果味野。最終引伸出一個問題：點解我咁想入大學？<br />\n<br />\n呢個post純粹想討論學中文嘅方法，應該唔會有罵戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，如果有高手知點樣做，跪求指點小弟一二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 讀緊一個自己鍾意嘅科但又唔係鍾意嘅內容，呢樣野真係好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想睇舊式小說：<a href=\"http://open-lit.com/list.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fopen-lit.com%2Flist.php&d=YWLSRs%2BcVshAsQ1%2FQDMmPaS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=d5ebbf9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://open-lit.com/list.php</a><br />\n想睇文史哲：<a href=\"http://ctext.org/zh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fctext.org%2Fzh&d=YWLSRs%2BcVshAsQ1%2FQDMmPaS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=9211692c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://ctext.org/zh</a><br />\n想睇現代小說：<a href=\"http://www.b111.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.b111.net&d=YWLSRs%2BcVshAsQ1%2FQDMmPaS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=52378215\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.b111.net</a><br />\n希望幫到樓主"},{"pid":"7fe96a6cb979862bc07f5d15a997b0f70405efda","tid":429709,"uid":17335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T08:05:46.000Z","msg":"古典文學可以睇我堆Post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中文好大程度都係靠自己睇<br />\n但點睇、睇邊個都係可以借助其他人"},{"pid":"70b58b84871f9d133e349f5601f0132b6daf50fd","tid":429709,"uid":17335,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T08:07:19.000Z","msg":"另外<br />\n中文系，唔係創作系<br />\n抱住學創作為主嘅心入中文系<br />\n絕對會係希望幻滅<br />\n年中唔少人入中文系之後勁hea<br />\n呢個係一大原因"},{"pid":"e583c60e21259988e67670a201b1cb8003e52401","tid":429709,"uid":129039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T08:09:42.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"e46026691540b3851fed9721363e6110e07671f5","tid":429709,"uid":143250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T08:15:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>古典文學可以睇我堆Post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中文好大程度都係靠自己睇<br />\n但點睇、睇邊個都係可以借助其他人</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有追巴打d post"},{"pid":"a872cc5e15e6938c4868ccba9b0cd9bacc27894c","tid":429709,"uid":143250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T08:15:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家做緊阿蘇狗 本科生有咩唔滿意請負皮，然後上一頁<br />\n<br />\n入正題：<br />\n小弟對文史野算幾有興趣，特別啲小學（音韻學）、詩詞歌賦、駢文、古典文獻呢類等，但現代同西方野就真係唔掂<br />\n最初想入大學嘅原因就係想提升呢方面嘅中文水平，達到可以出口成文、揮筆成詩嘅境界。同埋我都幾鍾意創作，例如改詞、寫詩、作故等。但問題就係能力太低，又唔工整又唔詩意，平仄押韻都係自己搞自己學，冇人教冇人討論，根本唔知岩定錯好定壞。<br />\n<br />\n例如想學琴，咁就去琴社跟